the Great Exhibition of 1851

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:22.460
was in process--

00:10:22.460 --> 00:10:24.140
it lasted for several months--

00:10:24.140 --> 00:10:27.500
an event of relative interest
occurred elsewhere in Europe,

00:10:27.500 --> 00:10:30.380
to be precise, in
Koenigsberg, Prussia.

00:10:30.380 --> 00:10:33.020
For the first time in
history, a solar eclipse

00:10:33.020 --> 00:10:35.480
was successfully photographed.

00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:37.220
I read this statement aloud.

00:10:37.220 --> 00:10:39.650
