photography in particular

00:10:42.230 --> 00:10:43.730
of all technological
developments

00:10:43.730 --> 00:10:46.820
was the likeliest to have
somehow impeded magic.

00:10:46.820 --> 00:10:48.921
Now somehow he was certain.

00:10:48.921 --> 00:10:51.170
It took me a while to calm
him down to the point where

00:10:51.170 --> 00:10:52.931
he could explain himself."

