If I do, they're buried so
deeply that I didn't even

00:50:28.390 --> 00:50:29.260
mention it to Neal.

00:50:32.950 --> 00:50:35.230
Now I'm starting to feel
like maybe there's some,

00:50:35.230 --> 00:50:36.730
but I've even buried
it from myself.

00:50:36.730 --> 00:50:40.330
NEAL STEPHENSON: You've probably
referred to important figures

00:50:40.330 --> 00:50:42.777
like the emperor, whatever,
who was mentioned.

00:50:42.777 --> 00:50:44.860
NICOLE GALLAND: Yeah, so
there's historical Easter

00:50:44.860 --> 00:50:47.300
eggs, so to speak, but not--

00:50:47.300 --> 00:50:49.917
no.

00:50:49.917 --> 00:50:50.750
No, I don't do that.

00:50:50.750 --> 00:50:53.200
But maybe I should.

